Photo, Conquistadores Give Charity a Run for Its Money: Thirty members of the 
El Camino Real High cross-country team hit the school track Friday, above, each 
running a mile leg during a 24-hour relay. The participants have solicited 
pledges based on distance covered, the money going to Covenant House 
California, a crisis-care agency for homeless and runaway street youths. 
