</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122290-0064 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 325814 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 22, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 29; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
