<TEXT>
<P>
A robbery suspect driving a stolen car was fatally shot in a gun battle with 
sheriff's deputies after a chase that ended in two-car crash near downtown Los 
Angeles Friday night, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
The chase began when deputies spotted a car in Lynwood that matched the 
