KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES 
-- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; RELIGIOUS ORGANIZATIONS; CHURCHES -- UNITED 
STATES; CLERGY; PEACE MOVEMENTS; MILITARY STRATEGY 
</P>
